<p>Menos de 100 bpm.</p>
</td>
<td style="border-width: 1px; border-color: #000000; border-style: solid; background-color: #eff5ff;" valign="middle">
<p>Menos de 100 bpm.</p>
<p></p>
</td>
</tr>
